data.description: Welcome to this stunning brick colonial in the heart of Dearborn, just walking distance from the beloved Levagood Park. This home offers plenty of great family & entertaining space, with a spacious living room when you enter the home, through the dining room, and into the even larger family room. The large galley kitchen is updated and offers two sinks and plenty of cabinet space. A large sunroom with a grill stove sits at the back of the home. Upstairs are three great-sized bedrooms with a full bath. The basement offers excellent storage and more living space. The large backyard is great for kids, pets & entertaining! Don’t miss this one!
